### Structured Output API Test Requests
### Test Spring AI's ability to map responses to Java objects

### 1. Get Movie Recommendation
GET http://localhost:8080/api/structured/movie/sci-fi

### 2. Get Multiple Movie Recommendations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/structured/movies/thriller?count=2

### 3. Generate Person Profile
POST http://localhost:8080/api/structured/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "senior Java developer with expertise in Spring Framework and microservices"
}

### 4. Analyze Technical Topic
POST http://localhost:8080/api/structured/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Spring AI and its applications in enterprise software"
}

### 5. Custom Structured Output
POST http://localhost:8080/api/structured/custom
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Analyze the benefits of using Spring Boot for microservices. Provide analysis, key points, and a confidence score."
}

### 6. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/structured/health

### 7. Horror Movie Recommendation
GET http://localhost:8080/api/structured/movie/horror

### 8. Comedy Movies
GET http://localhost:8080/api/structured/movies/comedy?count=5

### 9. Profile for Data Scientist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/structured/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "data scientist specializing in machine learning and AI"
}

### 10. Analyze Kubernetes
